FORM2: RIGHT OUTER JOIN dbo.BPSMT_PERSON AS P ON P2.PID = P.PID LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KRCDT_MON_TIME_ATD AS M ON P2.SID = M.SID LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KRCDT_MON_VERTICAL_TOTAL AS M2 ON M.SID = M2.SID AND M.YM = M2.YM AND M.CLOSURE_ID = M2.CLOSURE_ID AND M.CLOSURE_DAY = M2.CLOSURE_DAY AND M.IS_LAST_DAY = M2.IS_LAST_DAY
